Jimmy Failla.

The episode for Tuesday Oct. 14th was not capped. My DVR messed up. So all we have is this. If someone out there could be second stringer just to make sure that this never happens again that'd be great. You don't have to cap every episode, just the ones my dodgy DVR misses.
